nodes.text: Rancho Obi-Wan is the Sonoma County, California residence and storehouse of Stephen J. Sansweet, where he maintains the world's largest private Star Wars collection. It is covered in the online video Visit to Rancho Obi-Wan. It was featured as the site of an auction in the premiere episode of SyFy's series Collection Intervention. At the end of the episode, Sansweet himself bought a life-size replica of Captain Rex from Star Wars: The Clone Wars. Its content was presented at 2012's Celebration VI and at 2019's Celebration Chicago.
